<subSubSection pageId="184" pageNumber="185" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="184" pageNumber="185">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="184" pageNumber="185">
This 
<normalizedToken originalValue="species’">species'</normalizedToken>
name refers to the close proximity of the two median pronotal gland openings on the anterior pronotal margin (not, it should be emphasized, unique to this species).
</paragraph>
